outputs.output_descr: This project aims at assisting the Palestinian Authority to carry out its National Health Plan through the construction of the first and second stages of the Northern Wing at Princess Alia Hospital in Hebron. The project specifically aims at increasing access to quality hospital treatment and care for the population of Hebron District while contributing towards the development and improvement of hospital facilities in the West Bank
outputs.output_title: Dev. of Alia Hos. North Wing
